                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Get Your $25 Cash Bonus</h3>
              <p class="text-muted">
                Your <span class="font-bold">$25 cash bonus</span> will be deposited into your account within a few business
                days!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Referral Code Eligibility -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading text-center">
            Can You Still Use a Referral Code?
          </h2>

          <!-- Eligibility Chart -->
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
            <table class="w-full text-sm">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-2 font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Your Situation</th>
                  <th class="text-center py-3 px-2 font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Eligible?</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700">
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-3 px-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Never signed up for Wealthsimple</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-2 text-center"
                    ><span
                      class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 dark:bg-green-900 dark:text-green-200"
                      >✓ Yes</span
                    ></td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-3 px-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Signed up but never funded</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-2 text-center"
                    ><span
                      class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 dark:bg-green-900 dark:text-green-200"
                      >✓ Yes, anytime</span
                    ></td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-3 px-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Funded within last 7 days</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-2 text-center"
                    ><span
                      class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 dark:bg-yellow-900 dark:text-yellow-200"
                      >✓ Yes, act now!</span
                    ></td
                  >
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="py-3 px-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Funded more than 7 days ago</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-2 text-center"
                    ><span
                      class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-800 dark:bg-red-900 dark:text-red-200"
                      >✗ No</span
                    ></td
                  >
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <!-- TL;DR Box -->
          <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="font-bold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400">TL;DR:</span>
              If you funded your account, you have <span class="font-bold">7 days</span> to add a code. Never funded? You
              can add a code anytime, then you have <span class="font-bold">30 days</span> to fund.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Learn More Link -->
          <div class="mt-4 text-center">
            <a
              href="/blog/add-referral-code-after-signup"
              class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline text-sm font-medium"
            >
              Full guide: Adding a code after signup →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-8 font-heading">What is Wealthsimple?</h2>
    <div class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <p class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
        Wealthsimple is Canada's largest online investment platform, founded in 2014 and headquartered in Toronto. With
